From: Huacai Chen <chenhc@lemote.com>
Date: Thu, 15 Nov 2018 15:53:53 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] MIPS: c-r4k: Add r4k_blast_scache_node for Loongson-3
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 4.20.1
Git-commit: bb53fdf395eed103f85061bfff3b116cee123895

commit bb53fdf395eed103f85061bfff3b116cee123895 upstream.

For multi-node Loongson-3 (NUMA configuration), r4k_blast_scache() can
only flush Node-0's scache. So we add r4k_blast_scache_node() by using
(CAC_BASE | (node_id << NODE_ADDRSPACE_SHIFT)) instead of CKSEG0 as the
start address.

